findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges to change various parameters and settings, including tax, marketing, staking, burn, tresor, and liquidity fees, maximum transaction amount, wallet addresses, router address, and other configuration options.

findings.title: DoS with block gas limit
findings.description: The contract may be vulnerable to Denial of Service (DoS) attacks due to the block gas limit.
